      "ownerType": "Congress",
      "countryId": "usa",
      "profileHref": "/country/usa/congress/gary-j-palmer",
      "text": "Americans use a photo I.D. to open bank accounts, board flights, check into hotels, enroll in college, buy alcohol or tobacco, purchase medicine like Sudafed, rent cars, and more.\n\nWhy are Democrats against using a photo I.D. to vote?\n\nWe must pass the SAVE America Act. https://t.co/A8sHdDcvtN",
